# -----------------------------
# Genome Annotation Project
# -----------------------------
# Author: Susanna Schärer
# Goal: Keep scripts, summaries, and plots — ignore large data and intermediate outputs
# -----------------------------

# 1. Data (raw inputs)
Data/
!Data/*.md
!Data/README*

# 2. Logs and cluster output
Logs/
*.out
*.err
*.log

Results/**
!Results/**/*.png
!Results/**/*.jpg
!Results/**/*.jpeg
!Results/**/*.svg
!Results/**/*.pdf
!Results/**/*.md
!Results/**/plots/

# 4. Keep plots folder (contains final figures)
!Results/**/plots/

# 5. Scripts (all included)
!Scripts/

# 6. System and editor artefacts
*.tmp
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/

# 7. Containers and binaries
*.sif
*.img
*.bin
*.exe

# -----------------------------
# End of .gitignore
# -----------------------------
